Sentencas: Stable BaCe0.5Zr0.3Y0.16Zn0.04O3-delta (BCZYZ) thin membrane was successfully prepared by in situ tape casting/co-firing method for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Stable BaCe0.5Zr0.3Y0.16Zn0.04O3-δ thin membrane prepared by in situ tape casting for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The starting powders were BaCO3, CeO2, ZrO2, Y2O, ZnO for electrolyte and BaCO3, CeO2, ZrO2, Y2O3, ZnO for electrolyte and BaCO3, CeO2, ZrO2, Y2O3, ZnO, NiO, graphite for anode.
Titulo: Stable BaCe0.5Zr0.3Y0.16Zn0.04O3-δ thin membrane prepared by in situ tape casting for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The anode/electrolyte bi-layers were prepared by a simple multi-layer tape casting/co-firing method.
Titulo: Stable BaCe0.5Zr0.3Y0.16Zn0.04O3-δ thin membrane prepared by in situ tape casting for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The phase characterizations and microstructures were studied by X-ray diffraction (XRD) and scanning electron microscopy (SEM).
Titulo: Stable BaCe0.5Zr0.3Y0.16Zn0.04O3-δ thin membrane prepared by in situ tape casting for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The anode-electrolyte bi-layers were sintered at 1450 C. The electrolytes were extremely dense with pure perovskite phase and the thickness was about 25 mu m.
Titulo: Stable BaCe0.5Zr0.3Y0.16Zn0.04O3-δ thin membrane prepared by in situ tape casting for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The anodes were porous and no obvious reaction was found between NiO and BCZYZ.
Titulo: Stable BaCe0.5Zr0.3Y0.16Zn0.04O3-δ thin membrane prepared by in situ tape casting for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: With LaSr3Co15Fe15O10 (LSCF)/BCZYZ as cathode, the open current voltage and maximum power density respectively, reached 1.00V and 247 mWcm (2) at 650 C. (C) 2008
Titulo: Stable BaCe0.5Zr0.3Y0.16Zn0.04O3-δ thin membrane prepared by in situ tape casting for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells
